y text-2xl\">PageCub</span></a><div class=\"hidden items-center gap-7 text-sm font-semibold text-ink/75 md:flex\"><a class=\"transition hover:text-ink\" href=\"/how-it-works\">How it works</a><a class=\"transition hover:text-ink\" href=\"/samples\">Samples</a><a class=\"transition hover:text-ink\" href=\"/pricing\">Pricing</a><a class=\"transition hover:text-ink\" href=\"/faq\">FAQ</a><a class=\"transition hover:text-ink\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></div><a class=\"inline-flex min-h-11 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-ink px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold text-white transition hover:-translate-y-0.5\" href=\"/create\">Start a Book</a></nav></header><main class=\"page-shell py-14\"><p class=\"font-bold text-sage\">FAQ</p><h1 class=\"display mt-3 text-5xl font-bold\">Questions parents ask</h1><div class=\"mt-10 grid gap-4\"><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-line bg-card p-6 shadow-sm\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold\">How long does a book take?</h2><p class=\"mt-3 leading-7 text-ink/72\">Your book is usually ready in about 15–20 minutes. The status page will keep you updated as it&#x27;s being created.</p></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-line bg-card p-6 shadow-sm\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold\">What does my book actually include?</h2><p class=\"mt-3 leading-7 text-ink/72\">A complete 10-chapter storybook: 2 text pages and 2 illustrations per chapter (20 illustrations total), plus a title page, dedication page, opening note, and back matter with discussion questions and a draw-along prompt. Delivered as a PDF.</p></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-line bg-card p-6 shadow-sm\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold\">What illustration styles are available?</h2><p class=\"mt-3 leading-7 text-ink/72\">You can choose any style in the creation form: warm watercolor, soft painterly, classic children’s book, cute cartoon, whimsical fantasy, gentle woodland, bright colorful modern, minimal simple shapes, or Ghibli-inspired cozy. The style you choose is applied consistently across all 20 illustrations.</p></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-line bg-card p-6 shadow-sm\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold\">How much does a book cost?</h2><p class=\"mt-3 leading-7 text-ink/72\">Pricing is set at checkout. There are no subscriptions — you pay once per book. A price range will be listed here when launch pricing is confirmed.</p></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-line bg-card p-6 shadow-sm\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold\">What age range is PageCub for?</h2><p class=\"mt-3 leading-7 text-ink/72\">PageCub stories are written for children roughly ages 3–12. You can specify your child&#x27;s age in the creation form and the story length and vocabulary will be shaped accordingly.</p></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-line bg-card p-6 shadow-sm\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold\">Can I preview the finished book?</h2><p class=\"mt-3 leading-7 text-ink/72\">Yes. You can read the full finished book digitally before ordering any printed copy.</p></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-line bg-card p-6 shadow-sm\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold\">Can I order a physical copy?</h2><p class=\"mt-3 leading-7 text-ink/72\">Print fulfillment is coming soon — hardcover, approximately 48 pages. For now, PageCub delivers a high-quality PDF you can read, share, or print at home.</p></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-line bg-card p-6 shadow-sm\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold\">Do I need an account?</h2><p class=\"mt-3 leading-7 text-ink/72\">No account required. After checkout, you receive a private link by email to check your book&#x27;s status and access the finished PDF.</p></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-line bg-card p-6 shadow-sm\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold\">Is my child&#x27;s information safe?</h2><p class=\"mt-3 leading-7 text-ink/72\">Yes. Details you provide about your child are used only to create your book. We do not sell, share, or broker that information with any third party. See our Privacy Policy for full details.</p></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-line bg-card p-6 shadow-sm\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold\">How is the book actually made?</h2><p class=\"mt-3 leading-7 text-ink/72\">PageCub uses automated creative tools to write and illustrate your book based on the details you provide. No human author or illustrator reviews your specific book before delivery — it&#x27;s a complete, cohesive output generated from your inputs.</p></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-line bg-card p-6 shadow-sm\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold\">What if I&#x27;m not happy with the result?</h2><p class=\"mt-3 leading-7 text-ink/72\">If your book fails to generate due to a technical error on our end, we will refund or regenerate at no charge. Because generation starts immediately after payment and involves significant creative processing, we cannot offer refunds for books that were successfully generated.</p></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-line bg-card p-6 shadow-sm\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold\">Can I make a book for a grandchild, niece, or nephew?</h2><p class=\"mt-3 leading-7 text-ink/72\">Yes, as long as you are the parent or guardian, or have explicit permission from the child&#x27;s parent or guardian.</p></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-line bg-card p-6 shadow-sm\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold\">What information should I include?</h2><p class=\"mt-3 leading-7 text-ink/72\">The most useful details are warm and specific: personality quirks, what they love, what they&#x27;re going through, how they look, and the feeling or lesson you want the story to leave behind.</p></section></div></main><footer class=\"border-t border-line bg-card/70\"><div class=\"page-shell grid gap-8 py-10 md:grid-cols-[1.2fr_2fr]\"><div><p class=\"display text-2xl font-bold\">PageCub</p><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-sm text-sm leading-6 tex